name: henosyDrift
description:
happy henosy! move your mouse to create a drawing to celebrate the first 6 months of drifting through h=n to discover drawings, art and new friends. stop moving your mouse to develop the drawing at that position. your wallet id controls some drawing parameters

created in p5.js by AliaK, based on a modified drawing generator P_2_3_5-01 from the 'generative design' book
